snippet.title: BPM Boy - Teaser 1080p
snippet.description:
BPM Boy is a physics-based platformer, with influences from games like Marble Madness, Super Monkey Ball and DeBlob, all to a funky dynamic soundtrack. 

Coming soon to the Atari VCS, with other platforms to be announced.


Site: https://www.retroninja.com/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/14...



Discord: https://discord.gg/xzy3yTMS

Twitter: https://twitter.com/RetroNinja5
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RetroNinjaGames
